name: circumarctic-environmental-observatories-network-internet-map-server
notes: The Terrestrial Circumarctic Environmental Observatories Network - Internet Map Server (CEON-IMS) has been developed to enable and enhance the visualization and search-ability of a geo-database comprised of observational platforms and information sources compatible with CEON's mission. CEON-IMS includes a range of remote sensing products, maps, and information on historical and current research efforts - all of which are associated with envrionmental observations in the Arctic.
